title: Welcome Obama
subTitle: Yashoda agrees to be a surrogate mother to Lucy, an American lady. Unfortunately, during her pregnancy, Yashoda meets with an accident that jeopardises the child's life.

title: Chandrakala
subTitle: A family moves into their ancestral mansion to try to sell it off. However, trouble starts brewing when they experience supernatural phenomena and a ghost mysteriously killing people.

title: Masthi Maja
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the most funniest comedy scenes from popular Telugu movies is played back to back.

title: Badrinath
subTitle: Badri is the protector of Badrinath temple. However, when a woman falls in love with him, his guru decides against making Badri his successor.

title: Love Today
subTitle: Nikhita's father challenges her and Uthaman, the guy she is deeply in love with and wants to marry, to swap their phones. When they do, chaos erupts as their secrets come to light.

title: Chatrapathi
subTitle: Separated from his family during a conflict, a refugee embarks on a mission to reunite with his adoptive family. However, he faces several challenges after his foster brother conspires against him.

title: Raghuvaran B. Tech
subTitle: Raghuvaran, a jobless B.Tech graduate, refuses to accept jobs outside his field and falls into depression after his mother's death. However, his life takes a turn when he lands a project and falls in love.

title: Balagam
subTitle: A young man in severe debt believes that the only way to pay it off is through the dowry from his impending marriage. However, the death of his grandfather puts his plan on hold.

title: Baak
subTitle: Suspicious about his sister's death, Saravanan, a lawyer, tries to solve the mystery behind it, only to discover a mysteriously dark force at play.

title: Aaha..!
subTitle: Sriram, a carefree guy, becomes a scapegoat and takes the blame on himself after he discovers a secret about his elder brother, Raghuram.

title: Yenthavaadu Gaani
subTitle: An honest police officer works tirelessly to dismantle an organ trafficking racket. However, he is oblivious that the very man he hunts is his beloved's killer.

subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the most funniest comedy scenes from popular Telugu movies is played back to back.

title: Yevadu
subTitle: Satya gets a different face after he suffers from burn injuries, but a new face multiplies his problems. His ordeal begins when he leaves the hospital and has to deal with his lover's murderer.

title: Khaidi No. 150
subTitle: Seenu, a criminal, escapes from the prison and places his doppelganger, Shankar, in his place. However, upon learning about Shankar's noble mission, he takes up the cause himself.

title: Thug Life
subTitle: Gang leader Sakthivel adopts Amaran after a gang war, but years later, a survival from assassination sparks doubt. Soon, Sakthivel suspects Amaran, igniting a conflict of loyalty and revenge.

title: Vinaya Vidheya Rama
subTitle: Facing a menacing criminal kingpin, Ram fights to protect his family. Soon, he embarks on a daring mission to topple the villain and dismantle his corrupt empire.

title: Manjummel Boys
subTitle: After one of them falls inside a dangerous pit in the Guna Caves, a group of childhood friends muster courage to rescue him out of a space from where a return is next to impossible.

title: Vikram
subTitle: A special agent investigates a murder committed by a masked group of serial killers. However, a tangled maze of clues soon leads him to the drug kingpin of Chennai.

title: Evvarikee Cheppodu
subTitle: Harathi, who hails from a conservative family, falls in love with Hari. The couple then come up with a plan to convince her father who does not approve of their relationship.

title: Okkade
subTitle: A minister assigns Yugandhar, an honest police officer, to find a way to stop gang leader Subbarayudu and his followers who are running a parallel government.

title: Masthi Maja
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the most funniest comedy scenes from popular Telugu movies is played back to back.

title: Jakkana
subTitle: Jakkanna, who lives by the principle of helping those who have helped him, decides to assist a gangster who has helped him. However, his good deeds backfire when the latter decides to kill him.

title: Life Is Beautiful
subTitle: Srinu, a college student, relocates to Hyderabad and stays with his uncle. Later, he befriends diverse neighbours from different economic backgrounds.

title: Akhanda
subTitle: When the nefarious Varadarajulu plans to attack Murali Krishna, an ardent devotee of Lord Shiva, Akhanda leaves no stone unturned to defeat the evil.

title: Raju Gari Gadhi 3
subTitle: Ashwin and Maya, a couple in love, learn of the presence of an evil spirit in their life. Determined to bring their life back to normalcy, Ashwin sets out on a spooky journey to safeguard his love.

title: Baahubali 2: The Conclusion
subTitle: After learning that his father was brutally killed by Bhallaladeva, Mahendra Baahubali raises an army to defeat him and release his mother from the former's captivity.

title: Magadheera
subTitle: After waking from a coma with a new face, a man seeks vengeance on the thug who killed his lover. However, as he battles his enemies, he uncovers shocking truths about his identity and past.
